result.name: Café de Coral

reviews.text: I absolutely love this joint. For fast food it’s quite satisfying and surprisingly it has never ever disappointed me since I discovered it in 2013. I love it for breakfast, lunch and dinner. The staff are so nice and the seating is always clean and tidy. They usually have washrooms for you to use as well (unless you are in a mall then likely you’ll have to use the mall restrooms). I highly recommend if you are starving and cannot make up your mind about food choices. They will have more than enough to tickle your fancy for that meal time and then u can move into snacking on HK cart delicacies
it's ok. The crispy pork was a little salty
A popular fast food chain provides Chinese and Hong Kong-western style of set meals in moderate prices
I only like breakfast at C de Coral.Breakfast is excellent.There is so many choices not expansive.From 7 am to 1130 am.
Good price for the quality food that you get from this location.
